{"lastModified":1772031968464,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::6b8f1310-ab40-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0","yachtType":["Power Catamaran","Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia, Italy\n\nA prestigious catamaran in Cannigione. Discover the pleasure of renting Aquila 36 Sport, a motor catamaran ideal for a fun-filled beach holiday in Cannigione, in the heart of Northern Sardinia. With two spacious double cabins and two full bathrooms, the Aquila 36 combines sporty performance with exceptional comfort.\n\nThe aft area of the Aquila 36 is a real living room on the sea, designed to offer dynamism and comfort, with large seats that can be transformed into a sundeck and a practical cabinet with an external fridge and BBQ. Under the impressive Hard Top you will find a spacious galley and a table that can accommodate up to 10 guests, while the forward saloon offers additional space for relaxation and fun in the sun.\n\nInside, elegance meets functionality: luxurious double cabins with en-suite bathrooms, a refined and bright interior design thanks to the large windows, offering unparalleled privacy and comfort, typical of a catamaran that guarantees one cabin per hull.\n\nEquipped with a joystick, skyhook, air conditioning and generator, the Aquila 36 Sport guarantees smooth navigation and mooring, making your day cruise or day rental an unforgettable experience.\n\nCustomize your event on board the Aquila 36 Sport thanks to our expert organizer: every detail will be taken care of to make your every wish come true, making every moment on board absolutely unique.","blueprint":{"name":"AQUILA 36","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b8f1310-ab40-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::cddc41d0-ab42-11ef-8fed-f3c4d5e757ad/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b8f1310-ab40-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::cddc1ac0-ab42-11ef-8fee-f3c4d5e757ad/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b8f1310-ab40-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::cde2aa70-ab42-11ef-9243-995b212d